<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老奶奶向罗西走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是谁？” 罗西问，她看了看四周，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是从哪儿来的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是这里的山神。” 老奶奶说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“山神？” 罗西扬了扬眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以前管理这座山。” 山神说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这座山叫鸟鸣山，是个美丽的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山上到处都是花草和动物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山下的村庄住了很多人，一切都很美好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了什么？” 罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“几年前，山上刮起强风。” 山神伤心地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“强风吹倒了树木和房屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>暴雨不停地下，引发了洪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些可怕的风雨都是黑雨大王造成的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和他的妖怪军队占领了这座山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是他从我这里偷走的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村民和动物们都逃走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那以后，鸟鸣山就变成了一个危险的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太可怕了！” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我不害怕他，我现在就去除掉他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！” 山神说，“黑雨大王太强大了……也太危险了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我必须去！” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个妖怪抓了两个人，他要吃了其中一个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，有时他还会抓人吃。” 山神叹了一口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许是一个贫穷的农民，也许是一个富有的国王……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可惜我们什么也做不了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西摇了摇头：“他不是农民也不是国王，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是一个叫‘唐僧’的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山神大吃一惊：“唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？” 罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧正在西行。” 山神说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他想从佛祖那里得到真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真经可以帮助大唐的人变得善良，大家都希望他能成功。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是不用担心。” 山神笑了笑接着说，“我想起来了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧带着一个非常厉害的徒弟，没有他消灭不了的妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叫孙悟空，以前打败过天兵天将！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咬着嘴唇：“我见过孙悟空。但是有一个坏消息，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空现在在另一个世界，他帮不了唐僧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天呐！” 山神看起来很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 罗西抬头看了看山上：“所以……山神，我必须去救唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山神想了想：“也许我们可以一起救他，我有一个计划。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂？” 史密斯侦探在警察局总部的办公室打电话，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只猪和猴子逃出了监狱，让所有的警察都去逮捕他们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“史密斯侦探！” 布洛姆市长大喊着跑进办公室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大口喘着气，领带也松了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探挂了电话：“怎么了，市长？您怎么喘得这么厉害？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我从市政府……一路……跑过来。” 市长喘着气说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出事儿了。一群猿猴占领了美罗城！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>